### Get global activity feed
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/activity
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get activity feed (page 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/activity?page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get activity for a specific list
# Run lists.http > Create a list first to get listId
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/activity/lists/{{listId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get activity for a specific list (page 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/activity/lists/{{listId}}?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
